title: Test
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of employees, with a total of 6 data points.
Overall Number of employees has increased over the Year.
Number of employees is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2013, roughly constant from 2013 to 2016, and lastly slightly increasing from 2016 to 2018.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2018.
Max Number of employees about 4165.0 was recorded at Year 2018
Min Number of employees about 311.0 was recorded at Year 2011
